### Test Contract Admin Endpoints with Filters

### 1. Login as admin to get token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@busify.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Get all contracts without filters (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get all contracts with custom pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Filter contracts by status (PENDING)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=10&status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Filter contracts by status (ACCEPTED)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=10&status=ACCEPTED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Filter contracts by email
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=10&email=operator@busify.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Filter contracts by operation area
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=10&operationArea=TP.HCM
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Multiple filters - status and email
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=10&status=PENDING&email=operator@busify.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Multiple filters - status and operation area
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=10&status=ACCEPTED&operationArea=Đà Nẵng
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. All filters combined
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/all?page=1&limit=10&status=PENDING&email=operator@busify.com&operationArea=TP.HCM
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get contract statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contracts/admin/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
